<plot>In a cafe, two waitresses chat up customers. A chubby fellow tries to avoid fat and cholesterol. A white-haired woman orders a little of everything and then catches the eye of another older diner. A young couple feuds outside the cafe. A mother and her daughter wait for mom's new boyfriend. A young man enters, sits at a reserved table, and sticks a dynamite bomb to the table's underside. He leaves, pauses outside to set the bomb's timer remotely for five minutes, and walks away. His victims, two tough guys, sit at the table, get a call on their cell phone, and leave. The young couple enters and sits at the table, continuing their argument. The bomb's timer ticks down.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?428015</url></doc>
